ertel Thorvaldsen", "articleit": "https://it.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bertel_Thorvaldsen", "nameen": "Bertel Thorvaldsen", "articleen": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bertel_Thorvaldsen", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q5", "instanceofLabel": "\u00eatre humain", "gndid": "118622323"}], "wikidata_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q47812", "wikipedia_page_title": "Bertel Thorvaldsen", "added_wikidata_wikipedia_to_text_links": true, "_initial": "T", "url": "https://hls-dhs-dss.ch/it/articles/021965/2013-12-18"}